		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">In a <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=20685#20685" class="postlink">discussion about cleaning an NES internally</a>, tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Disadvantage is that you're likely breaking the law by operating unshielded RF equipment in the TV bands.</div>
<br />
<br /> <img src="./images/smilies/icon_exclaim.gif" alt=":!:" title="Exclamation" />  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_exclaim.gif" alt=":!:" title="Exclamation" />  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_exclaim.gif" alt=":!:" title="Exclamation" /> 
<br />
<br />Are you <em>nuts</em>? We write NES emulators! How much more illegal can this all be? What about all of the million's of ROM's that we have downloaded!!!

		

		</td>
